# 用户运行时数据(user/ 内由 WebUI 写入或运行时生成的个人配置,
# 含 API key / 个人角色绑定 / 个人覆盖提示词,不应进版本管理)
user/config.yaml
user/mcp-servers.json
user/roles-config.json
user/roles/
user/system_prompts/
# 模板/示例文件仍需跟踪,显式白名单覆盖上面的目录忽略:
!user/config.example.yaml
!user/mcp-servers.example.json

# 仓库根误生成的运行时副本(代码只读 user/mcp-servers.json,根目录这份是冗余)
/mcp-servers.json
/roles-config.json

# Ignore all user skills
user/skills/*
# Keep test/dummy skills tracked
!user/skills/dummy/
.browser_data

